fields.name: Crimes Red
fields.description: Firm and full on the palate with flavours of red currants, dark cherries and chocolate, complemented with vanilla.

fields.name: Diablo Black Cabernet Savignon
fields.description: Made with grapes picked at the exact moment of ripeness; delicious dark fruit notes; generous, flavoursome, dark, and mysterious.

fields.name: Faustino Rioja Gran Reserva
fields.description: Deep cherry-red and maroon tones. The nose is intense and complex with sweet notes of vanilla, spice and ripe fruit which follows through to the palate. Well structured and elegant with good acidity, leading to a warming, sweet, ripe fruity finish.

fields.name: Isla Negra Savignon Blanc
fields.description: Aromas and flavours of grapefruit, lime and gooseberry combine in this Sauvignon Blanc/Pedro Ximenez. Perfect for drinking with seafood and salads. Serve chilled.

fields.name: Las Moras Love Malbec
fields.description: Its aging in American and French barrels gives it a comforting red fruit jam flavor, with warm notes of vanilla and chocolate

fields.name: Love rose
fields.description: Elegant, stylish with a touch of pink. Med Ros√©'s delicate, fresh flavours will have you reminiscing about that sun-kissed skin, turquoise sea and those instagrammable holiday moments.

fields.name: McGuigan Black Label Pinot Grigio
fields.description: This Pinot Grigio is a refreshing white wine featuring delightful tropical fruit flavours. It is a well balanced wine with a clean citrus finish that is suited to a range of meals, especially seafood, fish and white meat dishes

fields.name: Graham Nortons Own Prosecco Frizzante
fields.description: A refreshingly crisp and delicate sparkling with a fragrant bouquet of apple, acacia flowers and hints of tropical fruits. Served chilled or even over ice for a glass of fabulousness!

fields.name: Santa Rita Chardonnay
fields.description: Has a crisp, fresh, un-oaked style. Its aroma and flavors recall tropical fruit mingled with green apple and an alluring hint of zesty orange peel

fields.name: Wolf Blass Eaglehawk Chardonnay
fields.description: Citrus aromas, melon and white peach flavours with a hint of oak on the palate

fields.name: Yellow Tail Shiraz
fields.description: Shiraz delights with mouthfuls of juicy red berries and a satisfying peppery spice finish.
